  "texts": [
    "The transformer encoder layer consists of a self-attention layer and a feed-forward neural network.",
    "The motivation for using attention is to be able to model dependencies regardless of the distance in the sequence.",
    "The attention concept has been introduced by Bahdanau et al. (2014), also referred to as \"additive attention.\"",
    "The transformer uses the so-called dot product attention mechanism.",
    "The self-attention layer helps the encoder to look at other words in the input sequence as it encodes a specific word."
  ],
